data.description: Welcome to your serene oasis in the heart of convenience! This charming duplex property offers the perfect blend of country living and urban accessibility, making it a fantastic opportunity for both homeowners and savvy investors. Nestled on a spacious lot with a fenced backyard, this duplex exudes a sense of tranquility, yet it's easily accessible to highway 6. A thoughtfully designed and open-concept living space seamlessly combines the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, boasting elegant granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar. With four generously-sized bedrooms and four well-appointed bathrooms, this property ensures ample space and privacy for all occupants. Each bedroom is spacious and inviting, providing a comfortable and peaceful place to rest and unwind. This duplex property offers the perfect balance of country charm and urban convenience, making it an excellent investment opportunity or a welcoming place to call home. With its well-appointed living spaces, stylish kitchen, and expansive backyard, it offers find comfort, tranquility, and accessibility all in one place. Don't miss the chance to make this beautiful duplex your own and enjoy the best of both worlds!
